The paper discusses the integration of machine learning and IoT, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and internet of things (cs.IOT). The paper also discusses the development lifecycle of ML-based IoT applications, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and system integration (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of ML techniques in IoT, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
